title: Kangdum Hurts Tree
body:
Ikari: *dressed as Sora, whacking a cardboard Heartless with a Keyblade* Bah, bah, bah! :D

Haida: *dressed as Xehanort, and doing a VERY poor impersonation of him to boot* I think the light…should live along with…the dark….wait, was that the goal the whole time? What’s the problem there? Wasn’t this guy played by Spock, or something, why am I doing this?

Fenneko: *dressed as Mickey Mouse, and doing a surprisingly good Mickey voice* Ha-ha! We own Star Wars now, bitches! Wanted a Zootopia world? Fuck off, you might get that in the fourth game, whenever that comes! Ha-ha!

Retsuko: *in her death metal state* YOU WALK AWAY, YOU DON’T HEAR ME SAY, PLEAAAAAAAAAAASE!!!!!!!

So like now’s probably not a good time to mention I’ve only ever played the first Kingdom Hearts game, that was back when I was a little kid, and I got stuck in Tarzan’s world, so I couldn’t progress any further, so maybe I shouldn’t have made this, but KH3′s a big deal right now, and Ben Diskin’s in the game, so EEEEEEEEEEEEEHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH
